        <h2>What We Are Building</h2>
        <p>
            A simple todo list application using ASP.NET Core MVC. The application demonstrates
            Controllers, Views, Models, and in-memory data storage. It supports adding new items,
            marking items as complete, and deleting items.
        </p>
        <p>
            Click the "Finished Product" tab above to see the working application.
        </p>
        <p>
            For more resources, check out the <a href="https://ngallego-linean.github.io/Linean-AI-Docs/" target="_blank">Linean AI Documentation</a>.
        </p>

