        <h2>Installing .NET 9 SDK</h2>

        <h3>Windows</h3>
        <p>Using Windows Package Manager:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-bash">winget install dotnet-sdk-9</code></pre>
        <p>
            Or download the installer from
            <a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet/9.0" target="_blank">dotnet.microsoft.com</a>.
        </p>

        <h3>macOS</h3>
        <p>Download and run the PKG installer from the official site, or use the command line:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -Lo dotnet.tar.gz https://builds.dotnet.microsoft.com/dotnet/Sdk/9.0.308/dotnet-sdk-9.0.308-osx-x64.tar.gz
mkdir -p ~/dotnet
tar -C ~/dotnet -xf dotnet.tar.gz
export DOTNET_ROOT=~/dotnet
export PATH=$PATH:~/dotnet</code></pre>

        <h3>Linux (Ubuntu/Debian)</h3>
        <p>Manual installation:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-bash">curl -Lo dotnet.tar.gz https://builds.dotnet.microsoft.com/dotnet/Sdk/9.0.308/dotnet-sdk-9.0.308-linux-x64.tar.gz
mkdir -p ~/dotnet
tar -C ~/dotnet -xf dotnet.tar.gz
export DOTNET_ROOT=~/dotnet
export PATH=$PATH:~/dotnet</code></pre>

        <p>Verify installation:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-bash">dotnet --version</code></pre>

